WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:04.060
Old man, when you wake up, I have to ask you something

2
00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:08.580
That's where we don't look like adults at all

3
00:00:09.240 --> 00:00:14.460
Do you think someone took your life after you posted the information online?

4
00:00:15.840 --> 00:00:17.620
My adults are ambiguous

5
00:00:17.960 --> 00:00:20.420
It cost him tens of millions in just a few days

6
00:00:20.440 --> 00:00:22.260
But I don't always feel normal

7
00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:30.900
The little master was hit by a car

8
00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:33.200
Brother, I'm in the hospital now.

9
00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:34.580
I'm at Jiangcheng Second Hospital

10
00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:35.560
Where are you?

11
00:00:35.560 --> 00:00:37.460
We are at Jiangcheng First Hospital

12
00:00:44.680 --> 00:00:46.740
Mom, I'm so scared.

13
00:00:47.080 --> 00:00:51.140
When I got hit by a car, I thought I'd never see you again

14
00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:53.160
It's okay, the doctor checked it out.

15
00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:54.980
You have a slight head injury.

16
00:00:55.040 --> 00:00:57.080
You can leave the hospital after two days of rest.

17
00:00:57.080 --> 00:00:58.540
I'm just afraid

18
00:01:00.040 --> 00:01:02.900
Silly boy understands you are there

19
00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:15.140
Mom, I got the jade pendant back.

20
00:01:15.440 --> 00:01:18.540
The people from my hometown brought it back for me, please take a look.

21
00:01:21.800 --> 00:01:23.100
I have seen it.

22
00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:24.660
What wasn't there that year?

23
00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:37.820
I never doubted it.

24
00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:39.180
Don't think about it.

25
00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:40.280
It's all over

26
00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:42.260
It's okay mom

27
00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:44.780
I never want to be separated from you again

28
00:01:45.760 --> 00:01:48.260
Ok we will never be apart

